<item>
            <title>[HIVE-23708] MergeFileTask.execute() need to close jobclient</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-23708</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;So when YARN use Https, MergeFileTask causes more and more Threads named &#8220;ReloadingX509TrustManager&#8221; in HiveServer2&#12290;The threads named &#8220;ReloadingX509TrustManager&#8221; does not interrupt&#65292;and HS2 becomes abnormal&#12290;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In MergeFileTask.execute(DriverContext driverContext) ,a Jobclient created&#160;but not closed&#12290;The issue cause above&#12290;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Hadoop 3.1&#65288;1700+ nodes&#65289;&lt;br/&gt;
YARN 3.1 &#65288;with timelineserver enabled&#65292;https enabled)&lt;br/&gt;
Hive 3.1 (15 HS2 instance)&lt;br/&gt;
60000+ YARN Applications every day&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
